---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Terms & Conditions — Eddie Miller Agency"
  description="Terms and Conditions of Eddie Miller Agency. Services, pricing, delivery, confidentiality and applicable law."
  canonicalUrl="https://eddiemiller.agency/it/termini"
>
  <Header />
  <main id="main-content" class="pt-32 pb-16 md:pt-40 md:pb-24 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 bg-cream">
    <article class="max-w-container mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-16">
      <div class="max-w-[65ch]">
        <div class="bg-sand/40 border border-sand  px-5 py-4 mb-10 md:mb-14">
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base font-sans text-stone">
            This is an English translation. The legally binding version is available in French at <a href="/cgv" class="text-terracotta transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-terracotta-dark">/cgv</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-[2rem] md:text-[3rem] font-serif font-normal leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal mb-4">
          Terms & Conditions
        </h1>
        <p class="text-sm font-sans text-stone mb-10 md:mb-14">
          Eddie Miller Agency · SIRET: 877 928 176 00024 · Last updated: March 3, 2026
        </p>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-4">
            Article 1 — Purpose
          </h2>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
            These Terms and Conditions apply to all online visibility services provided by Eddie Miller Agency to any professional client (hereinafter "the Client").
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-4">
            Article 2 — Services
          </h2>
          <div class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone space-y-3">
            <p>Services include:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
              <li>Online visibility diagnostic (free or paid depending on the quote)</li>
              <li>Optimization to help your clients find you: content writing, professional listing updates, directory submissions</li>
              <li>Monthly follow-up as part of the subscription</li>
            </ul>
            <p>The exact scope of each service is detailed in the quote or commercial proposal accepted by the Client.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-4">
            Article 3 — Pricing and Payment
          </h2>
          <div class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone space-y-3">
            <p>Prices are those indicated in the quote sent to the Client. They are expressed in euros. VAT not applicable — article 293 B of the French General Tax Code (CGI).</p>
            <p>Payment terms:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
              <li>Full payment upon order, before services begin</li>
              <li>Bank transfer or online payment via Stripe</li>
              <li>No work begins until payment is received</li>
            </ul>
            <p>For monthly subscriptions: payment at the beginning of each month, automatically renewed.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-4">
            Article 4 — Delivery Timelines
          </h2>
          <div class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone space-y-3">
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
              <li>Free diagnostic: delivered within 24 business hours</li>
              <li>Essentiel: delivered within 5 business days</li>
              <li>Complet: delivered within 10 business days</li>
              <li>Premium: starts within 5 business days, follow-up over 90 days</li>
            </ul>
            <p>These timelines are indicative and may be adjusted by mutual agreement.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-4">
            Article 5 — Client Obligations
          </h2>
          <div class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone space-y-3">
            <p>To ensure proper delivery of services, the Client agrees to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
              <li>Provide the information requested in the onboarding questionnaire within 5 business days of placing the order</li>
              <li>Grant access to the required platforms (Google Business, website) if needed</li>
              <li>Publish deliverables according to the provided instructions within the recommended timelines</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Any delay on the Client's part will extend the delivery timelines accordingly.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-4">
            Article 6 — Best-Efforts Obligation
          </h2>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
            Eddie Miller Agency commits to a best-efforts obligation, not a guarantee of results. Rankings on Google and AI assistants depend on third-party algorithms that are independent of any external intervention. The before/after visibility score serves as the objective indicator of the work performed.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-4">
            Article 7 — Cancellation and Termination
          </h2>
          <div class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone space-y-3">
            <p>B2B services are not subject to the consumer cooling-off period.</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
              <li>Cancellation before work begins: full refund</li>
              <li>Cancellation after work has begun: invoiced pro rata for work completed</li>
            </ul>
            <p>For subscriptions: cancellation is possible at any time with 30 days' notice. The current month remains due.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-4">
            Article 8 — Confidentiality
          </h2>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
            Eddie Miller Agency undertakes not to disclose any confidential information about the Client to third parties. Case studies used in marketing materials are systematically anonymized unless the Client has given explicit consent.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-4">
            Article 9 — Intellectual Property
          </h2>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
            Deliverables (texts, FAQs, descriptions, reports) produced as part of the services are transferred to the Client for use on their own platforms. They may not be resold or shared with third parties without prior agreement.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal mb-4">
            Article 10 — Applicable Law
          </h2>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
            These Terms and Conditions are governed by French law. In the event of a dispute, the parties agree to seek an amicable resolution before initiating any legal proceedings.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
